{"tid":678390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬逢國髮Gel風波　空勤工會轟濫權","createTime":"2018-05-26T04:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T07:41:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cc0cd757407375af93bdef29d1a4fee6efaeae43","tid":678390,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180526/20401815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180526%2F20401815&d=2aExcw5PoHOJBrg3cG3sSC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f184720d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180526%2F20401815&h=3d624ad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180526/20401815</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月26日 <br />\n<br />\n馬逢國髮Gel風波　空勤工會轟濫權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180526/large/a0802a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180526%2Flarge%2Fa0802a.gif&h=ce624bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■馬逢國（圓圖）所用髮膠品牌GATSBY，昨日在fb發帖指現時買定型箒喱膏送30克輕便裝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】建制派立法會議員馬逢國「撻朵」帶超量髮膠登機，違反機場保安規定。香港空勤人員總工會發聲明強烈譴責，指事件是前特首梁振英「行李門」濫權翻版，要求機管局採取措施防止再有權貴向機場人員施壓。<br />\n<br />\n香港空勤人員總工會聲明指出，馬逢國公然違反空檢守則，事件嚴重程度相當於2016年前特首梁振英涉嫌施壓，要求女兒梁頌昕遺留的行李可直送入禁區事件。再次凸顯權貴利用個人公權力挑戰機場保安人員的專業，肆意謀求自身方便及利益，有負市民對公職人員行為期望，更甚者是置公眾安全於不顧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGATSBY送輕便裝「抽水」<br />\n<br />\n總工會主席黎玉嬋批評馬逢國利用地位及人脈關係向保安人員施壓，事件被揭發後，又托詞大家對有關規定有不同理解，藉此為自己開脫，行為令人失望。總工會要求機管局應採取必要之措施，例如給予清晰、明確指示予前線人員，不能因檢查對象是公眾人物或公職人員而給予特殊對待。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員譚文豪去信立法會內務委員會主席李慧琼，按《議事規則》第16(4)條，要求在下月13日的立法會大會上，就事件提出休會辯論議案，預計將在下周五的內委會上討論。<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪在信中指出，公職人員自恃身份尊貴，妄自尊大，並引用身份向機場職員施壓來獲得個人方便，威脅航班、旅客等安全，打擊國際社會對香港機場保安的信心。<br />\n<br />\n此外，馬逢國所用髮膠品牌GATSBY，昨在fb專頁發帖指現時買定型箒喱膏，會送一支30克輕便裝，更hashtag強調「#30g可以帶上飛機」及「#時刻保持靚仔造型」，不少網民讚「靚抽」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n鄭耀棠被控不小心駕駛　聲稱無錢請律師　事主本欲放生：係長毛就唔放過佢<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n港媒北上遇襲　建制派阻休會辯論"},{"pid":"ad5ba13fa61ccb3a014a56db77b20ccfe32243a3","tid":678390,"uid":164608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"佢？Gel頂？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9b5d9b5ad1218488d818492f8a1cd6bab3872b","tid":678390,"uid":161945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"成 諗佢個頭要gel 咩？"},{"pid":"c85eb8d6ba623dae7c20690d4ee2ea1628374e0e","tid":678390,"uid":164608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢？Gel頂？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636fa6fdd0ff54c91569ea514952f81bf7acaeeb","tid":678390,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"200cc夠馬逢國gal幾多年？"},{"pid":"6fb9423a7747feffe0942b2f57fe9f16ca6fbc82","tid":678390,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"On9仔先用G牌"},{"pid":"0405d99ed23fee588c58e79cab20ba80a031b7a9","tid":678390,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:56:08.000Z","msg":"有冇指證放行馬逢國個高層出黎先？"},{"pid":"85e3fcb49d7e04b57cf05d6bdd984df6ade44f82","tid":678390,"uid":81021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:57:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MLR-GWRWJDA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMLR-GWRWJDA&d=2aExcw5PoHOJBrg3cG3sSC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0ebb8c9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MLR-GWRWJDA</a>"},{"pid":"1f8da5a8ac352d5e73a2a3a5967b71ea8c6ab9f5","tid":678390,"uid":19643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T06:07:17.000Z","msg":"咁少頭髮帶咁多gel上機 好可疑"},{"pid":"e4f06a22e952aec32b05eda8e2767f0e2ec30475","tid":678390,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T07:28:46.000Z","msg":"特權階級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c2289963d17e4ddf1d3396bfc85bca40ab56d3","tid":678390,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"636fa6fdd0ff54c91569ea514952f81bf7acaeeb","tid":678390,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"200cc夠馬逢國gal幾多年？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"可以做家傳之寶"}]}